  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BECOME WHAT YOU HAVE IMAGINED</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Rock Simulator 2, you’re more than just a collector. You’re an observer of time and nature. Unlock over 100 different rocks, each representing a piece of the world around us. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1949770/extras/5588c836530788fb40597524ce619932.poster.avif?t=1767753642\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1949770/extras/5588c836530788fb40597524ce619932.webm?t=1767753642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1949770/extras/5588c836530788fb40597524ce619932.mp4?t=1767753642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LEVELING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Growth is not a race. Unlock and upgrade your rocks, and with each step forward, learn to appreciate the slow and methodical pace.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1949770/extras/f7e8467afb93ebdad6aa41290c62c2b3.poster.avif?t=1767753642\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1949770/extras/f7e8467afb93ebdad6aa41290c62c2b3.webm?t=1767753642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1949770/extras/f7e8467afb93ebdad6aa41290c62c2b3.mp4?t=1767753642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MULTIPLAYER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience peaceful environments with friends. There’s no pressure here. Sit together in silence or chat while watching the sun dip below the horizon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1949770/extras/5674d892dc21e32e4af116610a47d550.poster.avif?t=1767753642\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1949770/extras/5674d892dc21e32e4af116610a47d550.webm?t=1767753642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1949770/extras/5674d892dc21e32e4af116610a47d550.mp4?t=1767753642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WEATHER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join friends in serene environments, watching the sun sink below the horizon. No need for words. A quiet acknowledgment of existence and connection. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >AMBIENCE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Let the soundscapes guide you. Listen to rain, wind, or gentle music as you immerse yourself in the present.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LEADERBOARD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Success is not only measured by speed but by endurance. How long can you simply <i>be</i>? The leaderboard honors those who understand that existing fully in each moment is an achievement of its own.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PUZZLES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There’s something hidden in the rocks.  Be curious. Pay attention. The answers reveal themselves to those who truly look.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BECOME WHAT YOU HAVE IMAGINED</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In Rock Simulator 2, you’re more than just a collector. You’re an observer of time and nature. Unlock over 100 different rocks, each representing a piece of the world around us. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1949770/extras/5588c836530788fb40597524ce619932.poster.avif?t=1767753642\" width=1170 height=390 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1949770/extras/5588c836530788fb40597524ce619932.webm?t=1767753642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1949770/extras/5588c836530788fb40597524ce619932.mp4?t=1767753642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >LEVELING</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Growth is not a race. Unlock and upgrade your rocks, and with each step forward, learn to appreciate the slow and methodical pace.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1949770/extras/f7e8467afb93ebdad6aa41290c62c2b3.poster.avif?t=1767753642\" width=600 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1949770/extras/f7e8467afb93ebdad6aa41290c62c2b3.webm?t=1767753642\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1949770/extras/f7e8467afb93ebdad6aa41290c62c2b3.mp4?t=1767753642\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MULTIPLAYER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience peaceful environments with friends. There’s no pressure here. Sit together in silence or chat while watching the sun dip below the horizon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb